Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是我妹妹的生日\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}It's my sister's birthday today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.48,0:00:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我6歲了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I'm six!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.08,0:00:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她得到了一個新的風箏\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}She got a new kite.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.92,0:00:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我答應媽媽\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I promised Mummy 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.80,0:00:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去外面玩風箏時 我會照顧好妹妹的\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I would watch her while we played with it outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.52,0:00:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該我玩了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}It's my turn now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.40,0:00:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的生日禮物\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}No, it's my present 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.56,0:00:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想自己放風箏\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}and I want to fly it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.28,0:00:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別哭 它在上面呢 看\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Don't cry. I can see it up there. Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.68,0:00:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太高了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}It's very high.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關系 我能爬上去的\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}That's all right. I can climb up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 傻瓜\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Twit-you. Twit-you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.28,0:00:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 聰明的貓頭鷹\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Hello, Wise Owl.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.80,0:00:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 聰明的貓頭鷹\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Hello, Wise Owl.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.72,0:00:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 \N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Twit-you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.16,0:00:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有傻瓜才會爬上去\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Only a fool would climb up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.12,0:00:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們沒看到警告牌嗎\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Didn't you see the warning sign?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.36,0:00:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有電危險\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Pylons kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.52,0:00:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別靠近這里\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Stay away from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.52,0:00:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會碰電線的\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I won't touch the wires.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.08,0:01:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不行\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}That doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.72,0:01:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風箏的金屬線是可以導電的\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}The electricity will be conducted through the kite's metal rods.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.60,0:01:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我的風箏怎么辦\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}But what about my present?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.72,0:01:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我們的風朋友能不能幫忙了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Let's see if our friend the wind can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.64,0:01:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 聰明的貓頭鷹\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Thanks, Wise Owl!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.04,0:01:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 聰明的貓頭鷹\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Thanks, Wise Owl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.28,0:01:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別做傻瓜\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Don't be a twit-you. 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.60,0:01:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要觸電\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Leave electricity alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.48,0:03:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 傻瓜\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Twit-you. Twit-you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.52,0:03:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你好 是奧利弗先生嗎\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Oh, hello. Is that Mr Oliver?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.76,0:03:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是德雷克·布蘭肯 住在鹿場那邊\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}It's Derek Blenkin here. I live on Deerfold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.88,0:03:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年你給我鄰居的短尾狗做過標本\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}You did my neighbour's bobtail last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫佩珀醫生\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Dr Pepper.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我是不是找錯了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Sorry, have I got the right house?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.68,0:03:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是做標本的嗎\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}You do do taxidermy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是這么回事\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Right. Well, what it is, 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.76,0:03:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們剛剛度假回來\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}we've just come back off our holidays
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安排了清潔工\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}and we'd left our cleaner
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.56,0:03:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來喂我女兒的寵物兔子 法拉利\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}to feed our daughter's pet rabbit, Ferrari.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.84,0:03:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉利是那只兔子 不是我女兒\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}That's the rabbit, not me daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她想給它喂點好吃的\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Anyway, she wanted to give it a treat,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長話短說吧\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}and to cut a long story sideways,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不小心喂了它一袋巧克力\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}she's accidentally fed it a bag of chocolate buttons
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后兔子就死了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}and now it's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在聽嗎\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不該和陌生人說話\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I'm not supposed to talk to strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們把它放在冰箱里凍了一宿\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}..we've had it in the fridge overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我女兒還不知道 她才五歲\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}My daughter doesn't know yet. She's only five.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能不能把它做成標本\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}And I was wondering if you could preserve him for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.84,0:04:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉利\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Ferrari.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.28,0:04:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不會看出來的\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}She won't know the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會跟她說兔子累了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I'll just tell her it's always tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我鄰居說你的要價比較便宜\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}My neighbour said you'd do us a good price.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.04,0:04:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用把它弄得\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I don't need it all dressed up
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.48,0:04:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像彼得兔那么漂亮\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}and doing ballet like a Beatrix Potter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.16,0:04:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會把它藏在鋪著稻草的角落里\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}It'll just be in the corner of the hutch covered in straw.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.80,0:04:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上沒人會看到它\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}You'll barely see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是還沒想好\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}It's just...we're not ready
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.40,0:04:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么和她聊死亡的話題\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}for the whole death conversation yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.80,0:04:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是該跟我媽聊聊了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}We've got all that to come with my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.72,0:04:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 非常感謝\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Oh, thanks very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了 給個折扣就行\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}As I say, any discount gratefully received. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.64,0:04:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且要是能便宜的話 沒有腿也行\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}..It needn't even have legs if that's cheaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.16,0:04:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就這樣\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高興認識你\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Nice to meet you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.36,0:05:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假期里有一天天氣特別好\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}One day on our holidays the weather was so nice
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.22,0:05:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就來到了海邊\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}we came to the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.80,0:05:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去海里游泳\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I want to go in the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.04,0:05:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽帶妹妹去劃船了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Mummy took my sister paddling
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開始挖沙造城堡\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}and I started to make a sandcastle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.04,0:05:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正玩得高興\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I was happy playing, 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.40,0:05:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個人過來跟我說話\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}when a man came to talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.52,0:05:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說我長得可愛又陽光\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}He said I looked nice and shiny,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.56,0:05:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問我想不想去看海星\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}and did I want to see a starfish?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.24,0:05:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得挺好玩的\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I thought that sounded fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:06:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 傻瓜\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Twit-you. Twit-you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不認識這個人\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}You don't know who this man is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.04,0:06:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他或許看上去很友善\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}He may seem friendly 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.68,0:06:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可未必有好心\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}but his intentions might not be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你媽媽是怎么說陌生人的\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}What did your mummy tell you about strangers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跟陌生人說話\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}That I shouldn't talk to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.44,0:06:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別當傻瓜\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Don't be a twit-you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.80,0:06:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別離開爸爸媽媽身邊\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Always stay safe with your mummy and daddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聰明的貓頭鷹什么都知道\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Wise Owl knows best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Mummy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Mummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.92,0:06:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Mummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是我妹妹的生日\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}It's my sister's birthday today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我6歲了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I'm six!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.00,0:07:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她得到了一個娃娃\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}She got a doll, 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.12,0:07:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一套茶具 還有一個風箏\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}a tea set and a kite.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.19,0:07:39.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就等媽媽回來\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Now we're waiting for Mummy to get home
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.12,0:07:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給她點生日蛋糕上的蠟燭了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}so we can light the candles on her cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就想點\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I want to do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.28,0:07:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道火柴在哪里\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I know where they keep the matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.56,0:09:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 媽媽\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Hi, Mum. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.72,0:09:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅尼\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Ronnie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.40,0:09:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都要睡了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I'm getting ready for bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.79,0:09:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在才8點一刻\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}It's only quarter past eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.40,0:09:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正喝酒呢 想起給你打個電話\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I'm calling you between Corries.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.92,0:09:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好吧\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我挺好的\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.84,0:09:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找過你 但你不在\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I came round earlier. You weren't in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.32,0:09:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去忙了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I've been busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.44,0:09:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要把一只兔子做成標本\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I had to stuff a Ferrari.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一只什么\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}A what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.12,0:09:51.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是別人的寵物\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}It's someone's pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們養過一只貓 你還記得嗎\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}We had a cat, do you remember? 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.92,0:09:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和喬安妮小時候養的\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}when you and Joanne were little.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.52,0:09:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫米姆西\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Mimsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.08,0:09:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們最后把它處理掉了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}We got rid of it in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.12,0:10:00.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它讓你得了哮喘\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}It made you wheeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.92,0:10:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它看你的眼神很輕蔑\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}And it had this way of looking at you all superior,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.64,0:10:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺你就像是它鞋子上的塵土\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}like you were just muck on its shoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.28,0:10:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓是不穿鞋的\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Cats don't wear shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.36,0:10:11.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明白我在說什么就行了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Well, you know what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是想確認一下\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Anyway I'm just checking
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你星期一還過來嗎\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}that you're still coming on Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.76,0:10:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經有三年沒回家了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}You haven't been in over three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.12,0:10:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪內托大夫的話還記得吧\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}You know what Dr Dinetto said.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.32,0:10:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他又不認識我\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}He doesn't know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他什么都不知道\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}He doesn't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.28,0:10:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能照顧好自己的\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I can look after myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.72,0:10:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你行的 我就是希望你能回家來\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I know you can. I'd just like you to be there, 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.16,0:10:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅此而已 為了我\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}that's all. For me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿靴子的貓 穿上靴子就得\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Puss in Boots, he wore shoes, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸會在嗎\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Will Dad be there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.44,0:10:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 \N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問過他 可他大概不會來吧\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I asked him, but he might not show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.88,0:10:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他就那樣\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}You know what he's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.96,0:10:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計你也沒和他聯系吧\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I don't suppose you've heard from him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.88,0:10:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們都是按自己的方式做事 是吧\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}We all deal with things in our own way, don't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.56,0:10:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答應我一定要回來\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Promise me you'll come.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}OK. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 回來之前別干傻事\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}And you won't...do anything silly before then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.76,0:11:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答應我\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.00,0:11:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答應你了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好 我明天再給你打電話 親愛的\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}All right, then, I'll call you tomorrow, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.52,0:11:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.76,0:11:08.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I love...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是她生日\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}It was her birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.36,0:11:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅尼 你這是為什么呀 為什么\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Why did you do it, Ronnie? Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.48,0:11:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明知道這樣不對\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}You knew it was wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.80,0:11:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都別說\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}You mustn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.12,0:12:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什么\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.52,0:12:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聰明的貓頭鷹什么都知道\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Wise Owl knows best.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.40,0:13:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我妹妹的貓 米姆西\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}This is my sister's cat, Mimsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一天它生病死了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}One day he got poorly and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.20,0:13:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟她說別擔心 它去了貓的天堂\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I told her not to worry and that he was in cat heaven now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想讓它走\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Don't want to let him go
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.96,0:13:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想讓它永遠留在我們身邊\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I wish we could keep him for ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.52,0:13:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不可能的\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}But that's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.80,0:13:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 傻瓜\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Twit-you! Twit-you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.76,0:13:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聰明的貓頭鷹\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Wise Owl!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.32,0:14:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么來了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.28,0:14:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子們 你們沒聽說過動物標本嗎\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Have you children never heard of taxidermy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.88,0:14:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動物什么\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Taxi-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.60,0:14:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,標本\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Dermy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.04,0:14:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是一種把你最喜歡的寵物\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}It's a way of keeping your favourite pets
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.28,0:14:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠留在身邊的方法\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}around for ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.36,0:14:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我教給你們看看\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Let me show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.30,0:14:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你需要 手術刀 一些鍍鋅電線\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}You will need...A scalpel, some galvanised wire,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.56,0:14:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刮刀和化學染料\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}a scraper and tanning chemicals.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.20,0:14:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用前務必一定要閱讀說明\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Always read the label.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 你需要先把皮剝開\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}First, you need to peel the skin off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在腿部和腹部周圍做切口\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Make incisions around the legs and tummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.96,0:14:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后慢慢的把動物皮從尸體上扯下來\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Then pull the animal's pelt slowly from its carcass.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.64,0:14:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用手術刀摘掉眼睛\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Then you remove the eyes with the scalpel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.16,0:14:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我能幫上忙\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I can do this for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在壁爐里焚化尸體\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}You can dispose of the body in an incinerator.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著 把皮膚用化學染料浸泡一天時間\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Next, use the chemicals to tan the skin for 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.60,0:14:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這正是玩游戲或者吃三明治的好時刻\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}This is a good time to play a game or have a sandwich.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.60,0:14:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 用泡沫做出個一樣大小的模型\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Next, make a body shape from foam,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.68,0:14:58.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用鐵絲固定住 站著原地\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}using wire to keep it in place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.84,0:15:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后把染好顏色的皮\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Then, pull the tanned hide
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,套在模型上\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}back onto the model.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.60,0:15:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像往它皮里塞香腸一樣\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Like putting a sausage into its skin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.04,0:15:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選個玻璃眼睛 以匹配你的寵物\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Select glass eyes to match your pet's
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.60,0:15:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕輕的塞進模型的眼球里\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}and gently force them into the sockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.08,0:15:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,適當調整其位置\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Scrunch and pull it into position
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:18.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用針線把所有東西重新縫好\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}and use a needle and thread to stitch everything back together
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.28,0:15:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉眼間\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}and, hey presto!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.80,0:15:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道怎么做后將變得很容易\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Easy when you know how.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.64,0:15:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 聰明的貓頭鷹\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Thanks, Wise Owl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它就和新的一樣\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}He's as good as new!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.68,0:15:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我們改主意了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Yeah, we've had a change of heart
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.08,0:15:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把法拉利帶回去\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}and I'd like to get Ferrari back, please,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用做標本了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}just as he was.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.24,0:15:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還沒動手吧\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}You haven't touched him, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.60,0:15:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的奧利弗先生在家嗎\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Is the real Mr Oliver in?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.24,0:15:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和鄰居聊過了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I were chatting to my neighbour
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.92,0:15:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說這家主人是個70多歲的老先生\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}and she said he's a gentleman in his 70s,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以肯定不是你 對吧\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}so that's not you, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.24,0:16:01.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你是誰\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}So who are you, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.20,0:16:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么會在這里\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}What are you even doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最好沒對它做什么\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}You'd better not have done anything to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.56,0:16:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是法拉利\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Ferrari!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.00,0:16:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就要把它帶走\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Now, can I have him back, please,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.44,0:16:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然就要報警了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}or am I going to have to call the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.20,0:16:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的天啊\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Oh, dear God!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.24,0:16:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什么東西\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}What the hell do you call this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.04,0:16:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太惡心了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}It's disgusting!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讓我怎么跟我女兒說\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}What am I going to tell my daughter now, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.60,0:16:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她要是看到這個肯定會做噩夢的\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}She'll have bloody nightmares if she sees this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死的僵尸兔\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Bloody Franken-rabbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等著警察上門吧\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}You want reporting! 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.08,0:16:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這瘋子\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}You're sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死的本該是你 羅尼\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}It should have been you, Ronnie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.04,0:18:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅尼\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Ronnie...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.40,0:18:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 爸爸\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Hi, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.16,0:18:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.64,0:18:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你嚇了我一跳\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}You gave me quite a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.88,0:19:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得把修窗戶的錢給我\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}You'll have to give me the money for that window, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.52,0:19:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝吧\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.40,0:19:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不該喝這么多的\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}You shouldn't drink so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.32,0:19:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才多少\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}It's only a nip.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛從皮克林回來\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I've just come back from Pickering.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩具博物館舉辦了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}They had a '70s weekend
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一場70年代的周末秀\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}at the toy museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.88,0:19:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了不少像我這樣的老家伙\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}A few of the old buggers like me wheeled out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.36,0:19:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷·布魯克斯\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Ray Brooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.76,0:19:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來自皮普金斯的奈杰爾\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Nigel from Pipkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.88,0:19:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是個笨家伙 \N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}One of the Bungles -
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.44,0:19:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過不嚇人\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}not the scary one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.32,0:19:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們玩得挺開心的\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}We had a laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.68,0:19:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去20多年\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I don't suppose you've followed
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.42,0:19:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該沒關注過我的工作吧\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}my career over the last 20-odd years?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.48,0:19:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你住的地方\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Did they have a telly in...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.08,0:19:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有電視嗎\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}..where you were,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.56,0:19:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說他們不許你看電視呢\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}or were you not allowed?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.12,0:20:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《聰明的貓頭鷹》拍完之后\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I didn't do much
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.24,0:20:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就沒做什么節目了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}after Wise Owl finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有過幾次劇目巡演\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Couple of theatre tours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.32,0:20:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和杰夫·霍蘭德玩得不錯\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Nice two-hander with Jeff Holland.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.32,0:20:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過在那件事之后\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Everything was a bit tainted after...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.92,0:20:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么都沒意思了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}well, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.80,0:20:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三四年前他們想做個重制版\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}They were thinking of bringing him back three or four years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.50,0:20:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用電腦動畫 做出來也是垃圾\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Computer animation. It would have been crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.12,0:20:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正很不成功\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Anyway, it all fizzled out, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我現在就做這個了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}..I do this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.28,0:20:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會相信有多少人\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}You'd be surprised how many people
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.12,0:20:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要留住過去的東西\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}want to preserve something of the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.36,0:20:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留住一份記憶\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}keep a memory alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.20,0:20:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定格某個快樂的時刻\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Freeze-frame of a happy moment. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.08,0:20:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做過最大的標本是一只山羊\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}The biggest thing I've done is a goat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.36,0:21:00.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花了我將近一個月的時間\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I spent nearly a month on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.84,0:21:02.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個小老太太帶著羊來找我\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}A little old lady brought him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.68,0:21:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她給羊取名叫潘\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}She called him Pan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.04,0:21:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也許是個女巫\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Probably a witch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.60,0:21:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我還從沒做過貓頭鷹的標本\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Funnily enough, I've never done an owl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.32,0:21:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我確實也不想做\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I don't think I'd want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說說你在這里做什么\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}So, are you going to tell me what you're doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.72,0:21:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你媽讓你來的嗎\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Did your mum put you up to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.04,0:21:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道周一是什么日子 對吧\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}You know what day Monday is, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周一\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Monday?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.52,0:21:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那件事\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Oh. That.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.44,0:21:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她要是活著該有50歲了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}She'd have been 50.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.92,0:21:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.48,0:21:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時光如梭啊\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Time flies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.08,0:21:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的信你收到過嗎\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Did you get my letters?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.12,0:22:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到過幾封\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Yes, I had a few.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.68,0:22:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒怎么看\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I couldn't read half of them. 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.08,0:22:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的筆跡太潦草了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Your handwriting's shocking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.48,0:22:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Did you never...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.72,0:22:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就從沒想回來看看我嗎\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Did you never want to come and see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.04,0:22:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你媽不讓我回來\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Your mother said not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.36,0:22:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說我回來只會讓事情變得更糟\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Said it would only make it worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.08,0:22:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是無法挽回了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}It's all water under the bridge now anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.12,0:22:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.80,0:22:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不該再內疚了 明白嗎 羅尼\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}You mustn't feel guilty, you know, Ronnie.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.72,0:22:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是個意外\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}It was just an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.20,0:22:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不怪你\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I don't blame you, 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.44,0:22:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心我的態度\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}if that's what you're worried about.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天是我妹妹的生日\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}It was my sister's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.92,0:22:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我6歲了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I'm six!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.80,0:22:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她得到了一個娃娃\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}She got a doll,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.52,0:23:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一套茶具 還有一個風箏\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}a tea set and a kite.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.88,0:23:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就等媽媽回來\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Now we're waiting for Mummy to come home
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.40,0:23:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給她點生日蛋糕上的蠟燭了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}so we can light the candles on her cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.76,0:23:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就想點\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I want to do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.76,0:23:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道他們把火柴放在哪里了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I know where they keep the matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.74,0:23:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.36,0:23:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不該玩火柴 喬安妮\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}You shouldn't play with matches, Joanne.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.68,0:23:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 聰明的貓頭鷹\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Isn't that right, Wise Owl?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.60,0:23:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聰明的貓頭鷹\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Wise Owl?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.78,0:23:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.08,0:23:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喬安妮想點蠟燭\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Joanne wants to light her candles
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.96,0:23:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我告訴她這很危險\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}but I told her it's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.76,0:23:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 \N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Twit-you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.20,0:23:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火柴盒上不是寫了嗎\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}What does it say on the box?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.88,0:23:31.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會自己看嗎\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Can't you read?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.08,0:23:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全火柴\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}"Safety matches."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.48,0:23:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不就行了 \N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.84,0:23:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全火柴很安全\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}They're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.16,0:23:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她想點就讓她點吧\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}If she wants to light her candles, let her light them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.24,0:23:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是她的生日\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}It's her birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.92,0:23:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 聰明的貓頭鷹\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Thanks, Wise Owl.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.16,0:23:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不等媽媽回來再說嗎\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Are you sure we shouldn't wait for Mummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.52,0:23:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不等媽媽回來再說嗎\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}"Are you sure we shouldn't wait for Mummy?"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.32,0:23:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么什么事都要問別人\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Why do you have to ask permission for everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.96,0:23:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你膽子太小了 羅尼 我的天啊\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Grow some balls, Ronnie, for fuck's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.12,0:23:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說臟話\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}He said "balls".
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.76,0:23:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}But... 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.32,0:24:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘了 聰明的貓頭鷹總是對的\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Wise Owl's always right, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.52,0:24:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在讓喬安妮許愿\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Now, come on...let's leave Joanne to make her wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.16,0:24:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我到樓上去\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}You're coming upstairs with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.16,0:24:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想留在這里\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I'd rather stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.44,0:24:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聰明的貓頭鷹什么都知道\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Wise Owl knows best.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.48,0:24:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Now, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.16,0:24:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進去\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}In there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.52,0:25:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐下\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.72,0:25:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅尼\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Ronnie...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.20,0:25:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你坐下\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Sit...down!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.12,0:25:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么把責任推給我\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Why did you let me take the blame?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.28,0:25:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 別糾結于過去了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Oh, let's not dredge up the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.80,0:25:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說你在從酒吧回家的路上\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}You said you were on your way home from the pub
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.05,0:25:35.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到房子著火了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}when you saw the house on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.52,0:25:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說你從窗戶爬進去救了我\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}You said you climbed in through a window and you rescued me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.64,0:25:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是英雄\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}You were the hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.04,0:25:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你說謊了 對嗎\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}But that's not true, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.52,0:25:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就在房子里\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}You were in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.00,0:25:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我在一起\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}With me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.44,0:25:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你肯定是記錯了 兒子\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I think you're remembering it wrong, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.00,0:25:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒記錯\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.04,0:26:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有事業呢\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I had a career to protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.20,0:26:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是公共信息影片公司的喉舌\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I was the voice of the public information films
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.40,0:26:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我女兒在火災中被活活燒死了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}and my daughter gets burned alive in a fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.88,0:26:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這和我的形象很不符\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Not very on brand, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.96,0:26:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說我該怎么辦\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}What was I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.56,0:26:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我信任你\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I trusted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.72,0:26:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很聽聰明貓頭鷹的話\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I always did...everything...Wise Owl said.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.96,0:26:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只是個游戲 羅尼\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}That was just a game, Ronnie.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.60,0:26:24.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什么不好的\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}It wasn't doing any harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.36,0:26:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也喜歡這游戲嗎\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}You enjoyed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.12,0:26:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I loved you,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.96,0:26:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也愛喬安妮\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}and Joanne.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.90,0:26:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Now...come on,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.14,0:26:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我這兒來\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}come and join me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.20,0:26:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別傻了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Don't be a twit-you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.76,0:26:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你老爸一個擁抱\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Give your old man a hug.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.20,0:26:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別傷害我\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Don't hurt me, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.92,0:27:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還想陷入當年的處境嗎\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Do you want to be put back in that place?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.02,0:27:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你住手 我就什么都不說\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Stop this now and I won't say anything. 
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.40,0:27:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.68,0:27:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會說的\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}But I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.32,0:27:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅尼\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Ronnie!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.20,0:27:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅尼 你什么意思\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Ronnie! What did you mean? 
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.84,0:27:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪兒\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.44,0:27:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找我媽\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}To see Mum.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.64,0:27:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把一切告訴她\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}I'm going to tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.72,0:27:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴她什么呀\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}T-Tell her... Tell her what exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.52,0:27:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.72,0:27:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不 今晚就算了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}No, no, no. Stop the night here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.52,0:27:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們再談談\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Let's just talk some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.56,0:27:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能去\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}You can't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.84,0:27:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅尼 你什么都不能說\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Ronnie! You mustn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.48,0:27:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聰明的貓頭鷹不許你說\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Wise Owl won't let you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.72,0:27:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們必須始終按聰明的貓頭鷹說的去做\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}And we must always do what Wise Owl says...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.96,0:27:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對嗎\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}..mustn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.00,0:27:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再是了\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Not any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.98,0:28:05.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅尼 你回來\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Ronnie, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.46,0:28:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 傻瓜\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Twit-you! Twit-you!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.44,0:28:20.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜 傻瓜\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Twit-you! Twit-you!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.72,0:28:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾吧\N{\b1}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\shad1}Get stuffed.

